  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个温控系统的流程图。核心逻辑是：设定温度、实际温度，中间有个比较节点，然后控制加热器的开关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n8",
        "n4",
        "n5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那n8这个比较节点，您希望用什么形状？还有n3设定温度和n7实际温度，这两个输入节点有偏好吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n8",
        "n3",
        "n7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "n3和n7用lean-r吧，像输入端口的感觉。n8是核心比较逻辑，用圆形带斜杠的那种，表示减法或者差值计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，n3标注为'nominal temperature'，n7是'actual temperature'，都设成lean-r形状。n8用双圆括号包裹斜杠。接下来n4温控节点和n5加热器怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n8",
        "n4",
        "n5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "n4叫'thermostat node'，n5是'heater'，都用普通矩形。n4根据n8的差值输出on/off信号给n5。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n4",
        "n5",
        "n8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下连接关系：n3和n7都连到n8做比较，n8的输出到n4，n4用on/off控制n5，然后n5的输出影响n7实际温度？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n8",
        "n4",
        "n5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，闭环控制。n5加热器工作后会改变实际温度n7，形成反馈。布局用LR横向流吧，从左到右比较直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n5",
        "n7",
        "n8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经设置flowchart LR横向布局。n4和n5都设成rect矩形。我注意到n8的连接有点特殊，它要同时接收n3和n7，再输出到n4。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n8",
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，n8那个符号确认是双圆括号里带斜杠吗？我想表达的是差值运算，不是除法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是双圆括号包裹反斜杠，Mermaid里写成((\"\\-\"))，表示减法节点，不是除法。视觉上是个圆圈带斜杠的样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。另外主题用mc吧，经典look。现在整体检查一下：设定温度、实际温度两个lean-r输入，n8差值比较，n4温控决策，n5加热器执行，最后反馈回实际温度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n3",
        "n7",
        "n8",
        "n4",
        "n5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "配置完成：theme设mc，look设classic。所有节点和连接都就位了。n4到n5的连线上标注了on/off，其他连线是默认流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n4",
        "n5",
        "config"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这就是我们要的温控闭环流程图。各元素关系清晰，从设定值到实际值的反馈回路一目了然。",
      "elements_involved": [
